## Components

### Buttons

#### Primary Button
```css
.btn-primary {
  background: var(--color-primary);
  color: white;
  padding: 12px 24px;
  border-radius: {{BUTTON_RADIUS}};
  font-weight: 600;
  transition: all 0.2s;
