### Mobile-First Approach
```css
/* Mobile (default) */
.element { padding: 16px; }

/* Tablet and up */
@media (min-width: 768px) {
  .element { padding: 24px; }
}

/* Desktop and up */
@media (min-width: 1024px) {
  .element { padding: 32px; }
}
```

